Get Clients Now 365 was created from the Get Clients Now podcast. Get Clients Now 365 contains precise and powerful strategies, tightly packaged so you can consume the content quickly.

When you decide to subscribe and listen to Get Clients Now 365 you'll discover new (and advanced) strategies each day that include online business, marketing, persuasive communication, subscription, membership-business model and sales coaching and training ... so you can get more clients ... sell more of your products and services ... make more money and create a business that will carry on your legacy.
